name: ULiftable.up_down
initialProofState:
f : Type u₀ → Type u₁
g : Type (max u₀ v₀) → Type v₁
inst✝ : ULiftable f g
α : Type u₀
x : g (ULift.{v₀, u₀} α)
⊢ Eq (ULiftable.up (ULiftable.down x)) x

name: ULiftable.down_up
